					Tags: <a href="http://ottopress.com/tag/javascript/" rel="tag">javascript</a>, <a href="http://ottopress.com/tag/php/" rel="tag">PHP</a>, <a href="http://ottopress.com/tag/wordpress-2/" rel="tag">WordPress</a>, <a href="http://ottopress.com/tag/wp-load/" rel="tag">wp-load</a>, <a href="http://ottopress.com/tag/wp_enqueue_script/" rel="tag">wp_enqueue_script</a>, <a href="http://ottopress.com/tag/wp_localize_script/" rel="tag">wp_localize_script</a><br />					Category: <a href="http://ottopress.com/category/code/" title="View all posts in Code" rel="category tag">Code</a>, <a href="http://ottopress.com/category/wordpress/" title="View all posts in WordPress" rel="category tag">WordPress</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;
					<a href="http://ottopress.com/2010/passing-parameters-from-php-to-javascripts-in-plugins/#comments" title="Comment on Passing parameters from PHP to Javascripts in plugins">21 Comments</a>									 </div>
